{"concepts":[{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/collectiveTitle","prefLabel":"collectiveTitle","altLabels":["collective Title"],"notation":"","definition":"common title for a collection of resources. NOTE: Title identifies elements of a series collectively, combined with information about what volumes are available at the source cite.","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/crossreference","prefLabel":"crossReference","altLabels":["Cross Reference"],"notation":"","definition":"reference from one resource to another","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/dependency","prefLabel":"dependency","altLabels":["dependency"],"notation":"","definition":"associated through a common heritage such as produced to a common product specification","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/generated","prefLabel":"generated","altLabels":["generated"],"notation":"","definition":"inverse of wasGeneratedBy where the domain resource generated the range resource implying that the domain resource is a temporal event, such as a data processing action, and the range resource is an entity","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/hadDerivation","prefLabel":"hadDerivation","altLabels":["had Derivation"],"notation":"","definition":"inverse of wasDerivedFrom where the range resource was derived from the domain resource","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/informed","prefLabel":"informed","altLabels":["informed"],"notation":"","definition":"inverse of wasInformedBy ","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/isComposedOf","prefLabel":"isComposedOf","altLabels":["is Composed Of"],"notation":"","definition":"reference to resources that are parts of this resource","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/largerWorkCitation","prefLabel":"largerWorkCitation","altLabels":["Larger Work Citation"],"notation":"","definition":"reference to a master resource of which this one is a part","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/operatedOnBy","prefLabel":"operatedOnBy","altLabels":["operated On By"],"notation":"","definition":"inverse of operatesOn where the domain resource is, or can be, operated on (i.e.queried) by the range resource which must be an agent (i.e. is something that bears some form of responsibility for the operation taking place) ","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/operatesOn","prefLabel":"operatesOn","altLabels":["operates On"],"notation":"","definition":"an equivalent relationship to srv:operatesOn from a Service to a Dataset","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/partOfSeamlessDatabase","prefLabel":"partOfSeamlessDatabase","altLabels":["part Of Seamless Database"],"notation":"","definition":"part of same structured set of data held in a computer","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/revisionOf","prefLabel":"revisionOf","altLabels":["revision Of"],"notation":"","definition":"resource is a revision of associated resource","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/series","prefLabel":"series","altLabels":["series"],"notation":"","definition":"associated through a common heritage such as produced to a common product specification","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/StereoMate","prefLabel":"StereoMate","altLabels":["Stereo Mate"],"notation":"","definition":"part of a set of imagery that when used together, provides three-dimensional images","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/wasDerivedFrom","prefLabel":"wasDerivedFrom","altLabels":["was Derived From"],"notation":"","definition":"the domain resource was derived from the range resource which must be an entity (i.e. not an actor with agency or a temporal event) ","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/wasGeneratedBy","prefLabel":"wasGeneratedBy","altLabels":["was Generated By"],"notation":"","definition":"the domain resource was generated by the range resource which must have been a temporal event such as a data processing action or a field survey","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]},{"iri":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype/wasInformedBy","prefLabel":"wasInformedBy","altLabels":["was Informed By"],"notation":"","definition":"The domain resource was informed by the range resource which must have been an Entity (i.e. not an Agent with agency or an Activity temporal event). This is a looser association than wasDerivedFrom and does not indicate direct derivation, as wasDerivedFrom does.","scheme":"https://pid.geoscience.gov.au/def/voc/ga/associationtype","schemeLabel":"Associated Resource Type","publisher":[]}]}